It may take a few weeks, when we only have one day a week to work with.<p>4 - if your dog is unable to attend the monthly schedule for any reason, there will be no refund/credit. <p>5 - As with all accounts, your credit card will be charged 1-2 weeks prior to the beginning of the month, generally on the third Sunday of every month for the upcoming month.<p>6 - We require a 30 day notice for all cancellations of ongoing schedules. function firstAppointmentCheck() {
  if(document.itinerary != undefined) 
  	document.itinerary.startingaddress.disabled = document.itinerary.firstappointmentstart.checked;
}
function move(change, index) {
	document.itinerary.change.value = change;
	document.itinerary.index.value = index;
	document.itinerary.submit();
}

function highlightRow(row,onOff) {
	color = onOff ? \'lightgreen\' : \'white\';
	key = row.id.split(\'_\');
	key = key[0];
	//alert(key);
	document.getElementById(key+\'_top\').style.background = color;
	for(var i=0; document.getElementById(key+\'_\'+i); i++)
	  document.getElementById(key+\'_\'+i).style.background = color;
}

function generateDirections() {
	
	//alert("Temporarily unavailable.");
	//return;
	
	document.itinerary.generate.value = 1;
	document.itinerary.submit();
}

function sendToProvider() {
	document.itinerary.generate.value = 0;
	document.itinerary.emailprovider.value = 1;
	document.itinerary.submit();
}

firstAppointmentCheck();
</script>

<script language=\'javascript\'>
function firstAppointmentCheck() {
  if(document.itinerary != undefined) 
  	document.itinerary.startingaddress.disabled = document.itinerary.firstappointmentstart.checked;
}
function move(change, index) {
	document.itinerary.change.value = change;
	document.itinerary.index.value = index;
	document.itinerary.submit();
}

function highlightRow(row,onOff) {
	color = onOff ? \'lightgreen\' : \'white\';
	key = row.id.split(\'_\');
	key = key[0];
	//alert(key);
	document.getElementById(key+\'_top\').style.background = color;
	for(var i=0; document.getElementById(key+\'_\'+i); i++)
	  document.getElementById(key+\'_\'+i).style.background = color;
}

function generateDirections() {
	
	//alert("Temporarily unavailable.");
	//return;
	
	document.itinerary.generate.value = 1;
	document.itinerary.submit();
}

function sendToProvider() {
	document.itinerary.generate.value = 0;
	document.itinerary.emailprovider.value = 1;
	document.itinerary.submit();
}

firstAppointmentCheck();
</script>

with your pet sitter or to be put into leased lockbox). We prefer to be able to hold on to keys for future use, so if you don\'t want us to keep them you will need to let us know where the key can be hidden after last visit. would like to print out a more reader friendly copy of the SC, you can find that under the Request Forms tab of our website. It will then take you to your bookings, so hit the profile tab and then it will take you to the fill in the blank section. <script language=\'javascript\'>
function firstAppointmentCheck() {
  if(document.itinerary != undefined) 
  	document.itinerary.startingaddress.disabled = document.itinerary.firstappointmentstart.checked;
}
function move(change, index) {
	document.itinerary.change.value = change;
	document.itinerary.index.value = index;
	document.itinerary.submit();
}

function highlightRow(row,onOff) {
	color = onOff ? \'lightgreen\' : \'white\';
	key = row.id.split(\'_\');
	key = key[0];
	//alert(key);
	document.getElementById(key+\'_top\').style.background = color;
	for(var i=0; document.getElementById(key+\'_\'+i); i++)
	  document.getElementById(key+\'_\'+i).style.background = color;
}

function generateDirections() {
	
	//alert("Temporarily unavailable.");
	//return;
	
	document.itinerary.generate.value = 1;
	document.itinerary.submit();
}

function sendToProvider() {
	document.itinerary.generate.value = 0;
	document.itinerary.emailprovider.value = 1;
	document.itinerary.submit();
}

firstAppointmentCheck();
</script>
